&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4516&quot; title=&quot;When a CachingStateStore is closed it should clear its associated NamedCache. Subsequent queries should throw InvalidStateStoreException&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-4516&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-4516&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: When a CachingStateStore is closed it should clear its associated NamedCache&lt;/p&gt;

